%md 

Great! Now we've got an idea of where our customers are coming from. What about the gender vs. age distribution? Using this information, we can understand what demographics we need to target better to pull in more customers.  

-----

paragraphs.text:
%md

Interesting. It looks like the majority of our users come into the range of 20-30 years old. We also seems to have somewhat even split between men and women in that range. However as we go furthur down the spectrum the data seems skewed and not as normal. Females tend to dominate the older ages, except for at the age of 50. Interesting!

------

Finally, we'll take a look at the interest categories of our users and how those are distributed.
